    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/b23721bfd34b0a041f7563da443f4b00.poster.avif?t=1765293750\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/b23721bfd34b0a041f7563da443f4b00.webm?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/b23721bfd34b0a041f7563da443f4b00.mp4?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在3D世界中冒险的横轴动作RPG。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决战将在100天后到来，要如何度过这100天的时间由玩家决定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中有许多可以自由打造的内容，每位玩家都可以找到属于自己的攻略路线。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由操控无数的刀剑打倒敌人，爽快的动作战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公、剑、据点、妹妹等等，种类丰富且充满可玩性的养成要素。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据这100天如何度过，将迎来不同的结局。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗任你“打造”，千刀流动作！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/c32534e1ab284dcc7c4a34e456015a50.poster.avif?t=1765293750\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/c32534e1ab284dcc7c4a34e456015a50.webm?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/c32534e1ab284dcc7c4a34e456015a50.mp4?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公不仅可以使用武器攻击，还可以使用武器进行移动与防御等等动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器将从一刀流开始，逐渐成长为最大的“千刀流”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要如何使用入手的武器和几刀流去战斗都由玩家决定，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照自己的风格控制无数种武器，尽情“打造”你的战斗场景吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏进程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100天时光任你“打造”，选择与决断的故事！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/741215252ad9151c364b5c746a017b98.poster.avif?t=1765293750\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/741215252ad9151c364b5c746a017b98.webm?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/741215252ad9151c364b5c746a017b98.mp4?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在100天后的决战到来之前，玩家将自由地度过每一天的时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既能不断战斗逐渐强化自身，也能够直接向强敌发起挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你甚至可以不投身战斗，只是享受和平的时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到最适合的方式度过每一天，“打造”属于自己的胜利之路吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏进程的王牌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> 连命运都能改写的“神剑之力”！！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/c00cb1c70db25b080ea7754b42c35ac6.poster.avif?t=1765293750\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220860/extras/c00cb1c70db25b080ea7754b42c35ac6.webm?t=1765293750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为主角的王牌能力，玩家可以借助“神剑之力”改写自己的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以将获得的道具改写成完全不同的物品，将眼前的敌人从现实中“抹消”，甚至可以按已推进的天数将时间整体倒回——这股力量堪称彻底打破常规规则的“作弊级”能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这张掌握在你手中的王牌，将打破原本为主角设定好的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在受限于 100 天的游戏进程中，善用这股改写命运的力量，亲手“打造”只属于你的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >养成元素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连妹妹都任你“打造”，姐妹情深成长系统！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辅助主人公进行战斗的，是唯一血脉相连的亲人——最爱的妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天真烂漫的妹妹可能会因为主人公采取的不同行为，或是变得更具奉献精神，或是变得叛逆，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有可能变得好奇心旺盛，也有可能变得热心于研究。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与敏感细腻的青春少女展开交流，连妹妹的成长路径都可以“打造”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发团队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总监：盐川 洋介</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >代表作：命运-冠位指定（Fate/Grand Order）、王国之心、最终幻想：纷争 等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色设计：黑星 红白</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >代表作：召唤之夜、奇诺之旅、刀剑神域外传 Gun Gale Online 等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作曲：石元 丈晴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >代表作：美妙世界、王国之心、最终幻想零式 等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
